<h1 id="factoring-setup" sourcefile="Solutions/factoring-setup.md" sourcestartlinenumber="14">Factoring Setup</h1>

<p sourcefile="Solutions/factoring-setup.md" sourcestartlinenumber="16">Basic settings of the facoring add-on.</p>
<h2 id="setup-of-factoring-add-on" sourcefile="Solutions/factoring-setup.md" sourcestartlinenumber="17">Setup of Factoring add-on</h2>
<h3 id="necessary-business-central-settings" sourcefile="Solutions/factoring-setup.md" sourcestartlinenumber="18">Necessary Business Central settings</h3>
<p sourcefile="Solutions/factoring-setup.md" sourcestartlinenumber="20">For the correct function of the add-on, it is necessary to set and create other settings in Business Central.</p>
<table sourcefile="Solutions/factoring-setup.md" sourcestartlinenumber="22">
<thead>
<tr sourcefile="Solutions/factoring-setup.md" sourcestartlinenumber="22">
<th sourcefile="Solutions/factoring-setup.md" sourcestartlinenumber="22">Settings</th>
<th sourcefile="Solutions/factoring-setup.md" sourcestartlinenumber="22">Description</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
